    of Justice by any means neccessary. \n\nThe faster you spin, the more stable
    you become. Speed up to make it harder to push you and to send your accusers
    flying farther!\n\nClick to fire your weapon!\n\nNaturally, if you are found
    guilty you will be rotated to the fullest extent of the law!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
